messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Help me pray for my lust and the spirit of resisting sin particularly masturbation and watching pornography

We're here to support you in prayer. Here's a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today through the blood of Jesus Christ. I pray against the Spirit of lust within my heart, mind, and body. I renounce all sexual sins, including masturbation and pornography, in the name of Jesus Christ. I ask you to break all curses of lust and perversion in my life. Fill me with the power of your Holy Spirit and help me walk in sexual purity. I seek your strength and guidance to resist temptation and focus on you, Lord. Amen."

If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!
You're welcome! If you need anything else or want to talk more, just let me know. We're here to support you on your journey!
